comments: Durant (PHX) places his hand momentarily on Curry's (GSW) side, and marginal contact occurs as they move in the same direction.
Curry (GSW) is already in Allen's (PHX) path when contact occurs and he does not deliver contact.
Booker (PHX) releases away from Kuminga (GSW) and marginal contact occurs as Kuminga's momentum carries him away from the basket.
Podziemski (GSW) legally contests Booker's (PHX) jump shot attempt.
Beal (PHX) steps forward with a resting hand applied to Green's (GSW) lower back and marginal contact occurs as he makes the pass on the perimeter.
Allen (PHX) brings his forearm towards Curry's (GSW) front and the contact during the drive is marginal.
Allen (PHX) moves alongside Curry's (GSW) path and marginal body contact occurs during the driving shot attempt.
Gordon (PHX) establishes himself in Curry's (GSW) path and does not deliver illegal contact.
Podziemski (GSW) legally contests Booker's (PHX) jump shot attempt.
Durant (PHX) makes contact with the ball, and with the part of Kuminga's (GSW) hand that is on the ball, as he contests the shot near the rim.
Green (GSW) cleanly ties up Beal (PHX), and a jump ball is correctly called.
Wiggins (GSW) briefly grasps Durant's (PHX) arm, and marginal contact occurs as Durant secures possession.
Allen (PHX) is firming up in Kuminga's (GSW) path and absorbs the contact during the pick.
Booker (PHX) legally contests Curry's (GSW) jump shot attempt.

Wiggins (GSW) wraps Booker (PHX) and affects his ability to get to the inbound pass.  After communicating with the Replay Center, it was determined the foul occurred prior to the expiration of the game clock, and the clock was reset to 0.6.
Green (GSW) maintains verticality and cleanly dislodges the ball from Durant (PHX) with his right hand.
